  "texts": [
    "Base IRT model does not have student or item networks, and scalar parameters in the neural network estimate the student and item parameters.",
    "We observed a strong correlation between the estimated parameters of the Base IRT model and those inferred using the Markov chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) algorithm, which suggests that the model parameters can be interpreted as itemresponse parameters.",
    "To obtain the estimated IRT parameters, we iteratively trained Base IRT model using the entire dataset and kept the model that achieved the best prediction performance.",
    "The scalar parameters in the trained model represent the estimated IRT parameters.",
    "Additionally, we compared the estimations of SAD-IRT with Deep-IRT model, which has been shown to accurately estimate IRT parameters, especially for small datasets."
  ],
